title: CEO Says Volvo Creating Jobs by Using Free Trade
description: Mar.07 -- Hakan Samuelsson, president and chief executive officer at Volvo Cars, discusses the impact of a potential border tax in the U.S., the PSA-Opel deal, the possibility of an IPO and his outlook for China. He speaks to Bloomberg's Matt Miller on "Bloomberg Markets: European Open" from the Geneva Motor Show.
